>>>>>>>
>>>>>>> Step 2 =E2=80=94 MCP Calendar Tool
>>>>>>> Capabilities:
>>>>>>> list events
>>>>>>> create events
>>>>>>> reschedule events
>>>>>>> detect conflicts
>>>>>>> suggest time slots
