>>>>>>>
>>>>>>> Hermes treats all of these as inputs into one system.
>>>>>>> 8.7 Notification Layer
>>>>>>> We introduce a central notification rule:
>>>>>>> Hermes must notify you when:
>>>>>>>
>>>>>>> action requires approval
>>>>>>> system error occurs
>>>>>>> email is high priority
