>>>>>>> mobile push
>>>>>>> email digests
>>>>>>> desktop alerts
>>>>>>> 8.8 Action Approval System
>>>>>>> We define three action levels:
>>>>>>> Level 1 =E2=80=94 Auto
>>>>>>> Level 2 =E2=80=94 Suggest + Wait
>>>>>>> Level 3 =E2=80=94 Require explicit approval
>>>>>>>
