>>>>>>> Action Level
>>>>>>> Read email 1
>>>>>>> Summarize email 1
>>>>>>> Draft reply 2
>>>>>>> Send email 3
>>>>>>> Create calendar event 2
>>>>>>> Delete data 3
>>>>>>>
>>>>>>> This prevents catastrophic automation mistakes.
